<div class="container main">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-3 stage_menu">
			<h3>What policy changes will you focus your advocacy efforts on?</h3>
			<ul class="nav nav-stacked">
				<li class="active"><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Formulate the real world problem as a goal</a>
				</li>
				<li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Formulate the policy solutions as objectives</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9 col-lg-9">
			<h2>What policy changes will you focus your advocacy efforts on?</h2>
			<p>Advocacy planning involves defining and building consensus on the key policy changes to be achieved. The strategic selection of a few key objectives helps you make an efficient use of available resources and maximize existing opportunities.</p>

			<div role="tabpanel" class="tabpanel">
				<!-- Nav tabs -->
				<ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
					<li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="#data" aria-controls="data" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Data Entry</a>
					</li>
					<li role="presentation"><a href="#explanation" aria-controls="explanation" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Explanation & Examples</a>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<!-- Tab panes -->
				<div class="tab-content" ng-controller="stage2Ctrl">
					<div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane active" id="data">
						<div class="bg_grey">
							<button type="button" class="btn btn-warning pull-right" ng-click="show_goal()">{{ btn_problem }}</button>
							<h4>Formulate the real world problem as a goal <i class="fa fa-info-circle" title="The goals are the big changes and benefits being sougth for women and children, or in services and systems, as a result of advocacy objectives. Goal indicates what will happen after the advocacy objective/s is/are achieved. You should turn the real world problem into the desired real world change you want to contribute to through your advocacy."></i></h4>
							<p>{{problem.goal}}</p>
						</div>
						<%= render "goal_modal" %>
						<div class="bg_grey">
							<button type="button" class="btn btn-warning pull-right" ng-click="add_edit_objective()">Add Objective</button>
							<button type="button" class="btn btn-warning pull-right" ng-click="list_policy_solutions()">Policy Solutions</button>
							<h4>Formulate the policy solutions as objectives <i class="fa fa-info-circle" title="The advocacy objectives are what the organization aims to achieve over several years (usually 3-5). It is the overall policy change that is desired as a result of advocacy effort."></i></h4>

							<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert" ng-class="{hidden: unrelated_solutions < 1}">
								<i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> <a href="#">There are still {{unrelated_solutions}} policy solutions without objectives</a>
							</div>

							<div>
								<!-- <p class="bold">Filter by Policy Solutions</p>
								<a href="#"><span class="label label-info active">ALL</span></a>
								<a href="#"><span class="label label-info">Amendment to the Penal Code to remove sanctions in the form of detention for sex workers (3)</span></a>
								<a href="#"><span class="label label-info">Revision of the National HIV Strategy (5)</span></a>
								<a href="#"><span class="label label-info">Health insurance policy framework revised to cover disadvantaged informal workers</span></a>
								<a href="#"><span class="label label-info">Increase donor funding on PMTCT</span></a> -->
							</div>

							<table class="table ">
								<thead>
									<tr>
										<th>Objectives</th>
										<th>Subtotal Key Contribution</th>
										<th>Subtotal Momentum</th>
										<th>Subtotal Comparative Advantage </th>
										<th>Total</th>
										<th>Prioritized</th>
										<th>Policy Solutions</th>
										<th class="text-right">Actions</th>
									</tr>
								</thead>
								<tbody>
									<tr ng-repeat="objective in objectives">
										<td>{{objective.title}}</td>
										<td class="text-center">{{objective.key_contribution}}</td>
										<td class="text-center">{{objective.momentum}}</td>
										<td class="text-center">{{objective.comparative_advantage}}</td>
										<td class="text-center">{{ objective.key_contribution + objective.momentum + objective.comparative_advantage }}</td>
										<td class="text-center">
											<i class="fa fa-check" ng-if="objective.prioritized"></i>
										</td>
										<td class="text-center">{{objective.solution_ids.length}}</td>
										<td class="text-right"><a href="#" title="Edit" ng-click="add_edit_objective(objective)"><i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o"></i></a> <a href="#" title="Delete" ng-click="delete_objective(objective)"><i class="fa fa-trash"></i></a>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</tbody>
							</table>
							<nav>
								<!-- <ul class="pagination">
									<li>
										<a href="#" aria-label="Previous">
											<span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
										</a>
									</li>
									<li><a href="#">1</a>
